heading: 2. The 26th day of July 2022 is specified for the purposes of paragraphs
text_raw:
2. The 26th day of July 2022 is specified for the purposes of paragraphs 
(a)(ii) and (b) of subsection (1) of section 12 of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 
2019 (No. 31 of 2019). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

24 January, 2022. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 28th January, 2022.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation). 

This Order extends the period for receipt of claims by the CervicalCheck 
Tribunal to 26 July 2022.
